The '''Valley of Blizzards''' was a geographic feature on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Alzoc III/Legends|Alzoc III]]. Located near a [[Talz/Legends|Talz]] village and its Imperial mines, blizzards swept through the valley.<ref name="TEGtPaM" />

